before calling ptype callback.

Fixes: 88eb1944e18c ("net: core: propagate SKB lists through packet_type lookup")
Reviewed-by: Edward Cree <ecree@solarflare.com>
Signed-off-by: Alexander Lobakin <alobakin@dlink.ru>
